name: Listened to Colorado beats TCU in stunning win, FSU crushes LSU + an undefeated weekend for Pac-12

content.html:
Stew and Bruce look back at an eventful week 1 of games including a stunning win for Deion Sanders and Colorado over TCU, Florida State crushing LSU, and an undefeated weekend for the Pac-12. To wrap up, the first-time starting QBs that impressed, and the return of shout outs.
